<!--<h4>Second Panel.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>śrī svasti śrīmatu yādavanārāyaṇa bhujabaḷapratāpacakravartti śrīkaṁdaradēvana
<lb n="2"/>yānaṁdasaṁ<supplied reason="omitted">va</supplied>tsarada puśya suddha pavurnna<unclear>mi</unclear> sōmavārada makarasaṁkra mūṇadaṁ
<lb n="3" break="no"/>du śrīmatu sarvvādhikari ca<unclear>vu</unclear>ḍiseṭiyaru <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> <unclear>yaseṭima</unclear>llaya ci <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="4"/>ya <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> yaragaṁḍa gajasiṁgha <unclear>maṭharamaḍivi</unclear>geyalāda kaḷegadalli Iṟidu meṟadu muktarādaru <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>
</p>

<!--<h4>Third Panel.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="5"/>Ānaṁdasaṁvatsaṁvararada puṣya suddha pavunnami sōmavāradaṁdu <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> <note n="312-1">Read saṁvatsarada.</note>
<lb n="6"/>kāṟaru mukkhyavāgi kalidēvara mūḍaṇa meyalu <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> dalu <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="7"/>ra<unclear>ṁ</unclear> saluttaire <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>
</p>

<!--<h4>First Panel<note n="312-2">This section is engraved at the top.</note></h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="8"/>© jitēna labhyatē lakṣmīsmri(mṛ)tēnāpi surāṁgane <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> kṣaṇavidhvaṁsini kāyē (<g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>) kā ciṁntāmaraṇē
<lb n="9"/>raṇē 
</p>

